{"id":139,"parent_id":124,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":139,"title":"Romans 15","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rom.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 15"],[".studySummary",["i","True Saints fellowship one another—Paul recounts his diligence in preaching the gospel—The gifts of the Spirit are poured out upon the Gentiles."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.1","order":"03.08.015.16513"},["b","1"],"We then that are strong ought to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"bear"],"the infirmities of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"weak"],", and not to please ourselves."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.2","order":"03.08.015.16514"},["b","2"],"Let every one of us please",["i","his"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"neighbour"],"for",["i","his"],"good to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"edification"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.3","order":"03.08.015.16515"},["b","3"],"For even Christ pleased not himself; but, as it is written, The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"reproaches"],"of them that reproached thee fell on me."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.4","order":"03.08.015.16516"},["b","4"],"For whatsoever things were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"written"],"aforetime were",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"written"],"for our",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"learning"],", that we through",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"patience"],"and comfort of the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_4e"},"scriptures"],"might have",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_4f"},"hope"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.5","order":"03.08.015.16517"},["b","5"],"Now the God of patience and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"consolation"],"grant you to be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"likeminded"],"one toward another according to Christ Jesus:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.6","order":"03.08.015.16518"},["b","6"],"That ye may with one mind",["i","and"],"one mouth glorify God, even the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Father"],"of our Lord Jesus Christ."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.7","order":"03.08.015.16519"},["b","7"],"Wherefore receive ye one another, as Christ also received us to the glory of God."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.8","order":"03.08.015.16520"},["b","8"],"Now I say that Jesus Christ was a minister of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"circumcision"],"for the truth of God, to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"confirm"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"promises"],["i","made"],"unto the fathers:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.9","order":"03.08.015.16521"},["b","9"],"And that the Gentiles might glorify God for",["i","his"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"mercy"],"; as it is written, For this cause I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"confess to"],"thee among the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"Gentiles"],", and sing unto thy name."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.10","order":"03.08.015.16522"},["b","10"],"And again he saith, Rejoice, ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Gentiles"],", with his people."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.11","order":"03.08.015.16523"},["b","11"],"And again, Praise the Lord, all ye Gentiles; and laud him, all ye people."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.12","order":"03.08.015.16524"},["b","12"],"And again,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Esaias"],"saith, There shall be a root of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"Jesse"],", and he that shall rise to reign over the Gentiles; in him shall the Gentiles trust."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.13","order":"03.08.015.16525"},["b","13"],"Now the God of hope fill you with all joy and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"peace"],"in believing, that ye may abound in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"hope"],", through the power of the Holy Ghost."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.14","order":"03.08.015.16526"},["b","14"],"And I myself also am persuaded of you, my brethren, that ye also are full of goodness, filled with all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"knowledge"],", able also to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"admonish"],"one another."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.15","order":"03.08.015.16527"},["b","15"],"Nevertheless, brethren, I have written the more boldly unto you in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"some sort"],", as putting you in mind, because of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"grace"],"that is given to me of God,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.16","order":"03.08.015.16528"},["b","16"],"That I should be the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"minister"],"of Jesus Christ to the Gentiles, ministering the gospel of God, that the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"offering up"],"of the Gentiles might be acceptable, being",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"sanctified"],"by the Holy Ghost."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.17","order":"03.08.015.16529"},["b","17"],"I have therefore whereof I may",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"glory"],"through Jesus Christ in those things which pertain to God."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.18","order":"03.08.015.16530"},["b","18"],"For I will not dare to speak of any of those things which Christ hath not wrought by me, to make the Gentiles obedient, by word and deed,"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.19","order":"03.08.015.16531"},["b","19"],"Through mighty",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"signs"],"and wonders, by the power of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"Spirit"],"of God; so that from Jerusalem, and round about unto Illyricum, I have fully preached the gospel of Christ."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.20","order":"03.08.015.16532"},["b","20"],"Yea, so have I strived to preach the gospel, not where Christ was named, lest I should build upon another man’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"foundation"],":"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.21","order":"03.08.015.16533"},["b","21"],"But as it is written, To whom he was not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"spoken"],"of, they shall see: and they that have not heard shall understand."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.22","order":"03.08.015.16534"},["b","22"],"For which cause also I have been much",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"hindered"],"from coming to you."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.23","order":"03.08.015.16535"},["b","23"],"But now having no more",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"place"],"in these parts, and having a great desire these many years to come unto you;"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.24","order":"03.08.015.16536"},["b","24"],"Whensoever I take my journey into Spain, I will come to you: for I trust to see you in my journey, and to be brought on my way thitherward by you, if first I be somewhat filled with your",["i","company."]],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.25","order":"03.08.015.16537"},["b","25"],"But now I go unto Jerusalem to minister unto the saints."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.26","order":"03.08.015.16538"},["b","26"],"For it hath pleased them of Macedonia and Achaia to make a certain",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"contribution"],"for the poor saints which are at Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.27","order":"03.08.015.16539"},["b","27"],"It hath pleased them verily; and their debtors they are. For if the Gentiles have been made partakers of their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"spiritual"],"things, their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"duty"],"is also to minister unto them in",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_27c"},"carnal"],"things."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.28","order":"03.08.015.16540"},["b","28"],"When therefore I have performed this, and have sealed to them this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"fruit"],", I will come by you into Spain."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.29","order":"03.08.015.16541"},["b","29"],"And I am sure that, when I come unto you, I shall come in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"fulness"],"of the blessing of the gospel of Christ."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.30","order":"03.08.015.16542"},["b","30"],"Now I beseech you, brethren, for the Lord Jesus Christ’s sake, and for the love of the Spirit, that ye strive together with me in",["i","your"],"prayers to God for me;"],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.31","order":"03.08.015.16543"},["b","31"],"That I may be delivered from them that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"do not believe"],"in Judæa; and that my service which",["i","I have"],"for Jerusalem may be accepted of the saints;"],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.32","order":"03.08.015.16544"},["b","32"],"That I may come unto you with joy by the will of God, and may with you be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"refreshed"],"."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.33","order":"03.08.015.16545"},["b","33"],"Now the God of peace",["i","be"],"with you all. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.1a","order":"03.08.015.16546"},["b","1a"],["span.small","GR"],"remove, endure, bear with.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/31.33"},"Alma 31:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.1b","order":"03.08.015.16548"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/14.1.1-3"},"Rom. 14:1 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.2a","order":"03.08.015.16550"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/neighbor"},"TG Neighbor"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.2b","order":"03.08.015.16552"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/edification"},"TG Edification"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.3a","order":"03.08.015.16554"},["b","3a"],["span.small","GR"],"revilings, insults.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reproach"},"TG Reproach"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.4a","order":"03.08.015.16556"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/10.11"},"1 Cor. 10:11"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-writing-of"},"TG Scriptures, Writing of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.4b","order":"03.08.015.16558"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.10"},"1 Cor. 9:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.4c","order":"03.08.015.16560"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-value-of"},"TG Scriptures, Value of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/understanding"},"Understanding"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.4d","order":"03.08.015.16562"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/patience"},"TG Patience"],"."],["div",{"id":"4e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.4e","order":"03.08.015.16564"},["b","4e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-study-of"},"TG Scriptures, Study of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.4f","order":"03.08.015.16566"},["b","4f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hope"},"TG Hope"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.5a","order":"03.08.015.16568"},["b","5a"],["span.small","GR"],"comfort."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.5b","order":"03.08.015.16570"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/1.10.9-16"},"1 Cor. 1:10 (9–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/5.13.13-15"},"1 Thes. 5:13 (13–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/18.21"},"Mosiah 18:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.6a","order":"03.08.015.16572"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-divine-sonship"},"TG Jesus Christ, Divine Sonship"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.8a","order":"03.08.015.16574"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/circumcision"},"TG Circumcision"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.8b","order":"03.08.015.16576"},["b","8b"],["span.small","GR"],"establish, make constant."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.8c","order":"03.08.015.16578"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.20"},"2 Cor. 1:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.9a","order":"03.08.015.16580"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-mercy-of"},"TG God, Mercy of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.9b","order":"03.08.015.16582"},["b","9b"],["span.small","GR"],"profess openly, praise."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.9c","order":"03.08.015.16584"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.49"},"Ps. 18:49"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.10a","order":"03.08.015.16586"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.15.1-19"},"Acts 9:15 (1–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/30.2.1-2"},"3 Ne. 30:2 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.12a","order":"03.08.015.16588"},["b","12a"],["span.small","IE"],"Isaiah."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.12b","order":"03.08.015.16590"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-davidic-descent-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Davidic Descent of"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.13a","order":"03.08.015.16592"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace-of-god"},"TG Peace of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.13b","order":"03.08.015.16594"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hope"},"TG Hope"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.14a","order":"03.08.015.16596"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/knowledge"},"TG Knowledge"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.14b","order":"03.08.015.16598"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/warn"},"TG Warn"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.15a","order":"03.08.015.16600"},["b","15a"],["span.small","GR"],"part."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.15b","order":"03.08.015.16602"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.16a","order":"03.08.015.16604"},["b","16a"],["span.small","GR"],"servant at one’s own expense."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.16b","order":"03.08.015.16606"},["b","16b"],["span.small","GR"],"sacrifice, offering."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.16c","order":"03.08.015.16608"},["b","16c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.17a","order":"03.08.015.16610"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/26.16.16,35"},"Alma 26:16 (16, 35)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.19a","order":"03.08.015.16612"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/9.19.19-21"},"Morm. 9:19 (19–21)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.10.7-10"},"D&C 63:10 (7–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.19b","order":"03.08.015.16614"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-spirit-of"},"TG God, Spirit of"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.20a","order":"03.08.015.16616"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.15"},"2 Cor. 10:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/52.33"},"D&C 52:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.21a","order":"03.08.015.16618"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/52.15"},"Isa. 52:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.22a","order":"03.08.015.16620"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/1.13"},"Rom. 1:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.23a","order":"03.08.015.16622"},["b","23a"],["span.small","GR"],"opportunity."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.26a","order":"03.08.015.16624"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/almsgiving"},"TG Almsgiving"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/welfare"},"Welfare"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.27a","order":"03.08.015.16626"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.11"},"1 Cor. 9:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.27b","order":"03.08.015.16628"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/duty"},"TG Duty"],"."],["div",{"id":"27c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.27c","order":"03.08.015.16630"},["b","27c"],["span.small","GR"],"material, temporal."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.28a","order":"03.08.015.16632"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.17"},"Philip. 4:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/titus/3.14"},"Titus 3:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.29a","order":"03.08.015.16634"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.23"},"D&C 1:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/14.10"},"14:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.17"},"35:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.11.11-18"},"39:11 (11–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.12"},"42:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.34"},"JS—H 1:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.31a","order":"03.08.015.16636"},["b","31a"],["span.small","GR"],"refuse belief or obedience."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.32a","order":"03.08.015.16638"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/7.13"},"2 Cor. 7:13"],"."]]}
